/****  Select pr. fysisk fil *********************************/
SELECT  Koeredoegn_BKEY, count(*)
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://datalakegen2atlasdev.dfs.core.windows.net/zone-connected/protal/DM/dm_fact_protal_tog_litra_2022_01/A23EDA79-76A4-4506-ADF4-04FC0AEC099C_417_0-16.parquet',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) AS [result]
GROUP BY Koeredoegn_BKEY
ORDER BY KoereDoegn_BKEY
GO

/***** select 1 dag og 1 tog hvor opdelt PR. MD ********/

FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://datalakegen2atlasdev.dfs.core.windows.net/zone-connected/protal/DM/dm_fact_protal_tog_litra_2022_01',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) AS [result]
WHERE KoereDoegn_BKEY = 20220110
AND TogNr = 10
ORDER BY KoereDoegn_BKEY, TogNr, Lokation_sekvens
GO
